        {
            "title": "港股續尋底跌近2%  最多跌538點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">午後港股尋底，恒生指數低見26535，挫538點或1.99%，為暫時低位，現報26539，跌533點或1.97%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌183點或3.07%，報5797點 ; 恒生國企指數跌214點或2.24%，報9384點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"> 大市成交1979.46億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度(09888)跌7.45%，報116.8元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東健康(06618)升5.89%，報68.3元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15425538-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e7%ba%8c%e5%b0%8b%e5%ba%95%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%912-%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a%e8%b7%8c538%e9%bb%9e",
