        {
            "title": "A股全日低位收市  深股跌逾1.9%  創板跌逾2.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後跌破上午低位，滬深均以全日低位收市，深股跌逾1.9%，創業板指數跌逾2.8%，兩市成交合計19580.79億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數全日跌39點或0.97%，報4022點，今早開市報4007.13點，跌0.56%，上午中段曾倒升，見4034點，升5點或0.12%，為全日高位，午後跌破上午低位，以全日低位收市，全日成交8379.7億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日跌260點或1.93%，報13216，今早開市報13323.45點，跌1.14%，上午見13394，跌82點或0.61%，為全日高位，午後跌破上午低位，並以全日低位收市，全日成交11201.09億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日跌73點或1.57%，報4628點，今早開市報4663.32點，跌0.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌90點或2.82%，報3111點，今早開市報3145.92點，跌1.74%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15425507-a%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e4%bd%8e%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1-9-%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be2-8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 15:20:20",
